# Techno SMS Enterprise — Full Website Project (NO JS • Hard‑coded Responsive)

Below are all project files. Put them in a folder (e.g., `techno-sms-site/`) exactly as named. This version has **no hamburger**, **no JavaScript**, and uses pure CSS media queries. All nav links are always visible.












---

