/* =============================
   Quick Start
   ============================= */
/* 1) Create folder `techno-sms-site/`
   2) Inside it, add the files above with same names (keep `assets/` folder)
   3) Open `index.html` in your browser
   4) Replace `assets/logo-placeholder.svg` with your actual logo file (same name or update <img> src)
   5) Swap Unsplash images with your own product photos when ready
   6) Upload folder to hosting (TeleportHQ/Netlify/GitHub Pages/Vercel)
*/
